	step 3.2 : Add Persistance.xml in OtherResources -> META-INF (create folder) -> persistance.xml
	
	step 3.3 : Add PublicKey and payara-mp-jwt.properties file

	step 3.4 : create Entity Class from Database

		step 3.4.1: remove @XmlRoolElement and @XmlTransient and changes to @JsonbTransient
	
	step 3.5 : create Model class 

	step 3.6 : create StockResources (Rest class)

	step 3.7 : Bootstarp.java @LoginConfig and @DeclareRoles add annotation

	

Step 4 : Create ProductResourcesApp

