Step 5 : Create ShopClientApp

	step 5.1 : Add Depedency of jwt and jakartaee (if already then not)

	step 5.2 : Add PrivateKey in OtherResources

	step 5.3 : create Project Package  and in that package Create two class one is MyCredentials and second is DatabaseIdentityStoreHandler Class

	step 5.4 : put Token package in SourcePackages from sir

	step 5.5 : Add HttpAuthenticationMechanism Class

	step 5.6 : create Product Client

	step 5.7 : create Model class for Product for getter and setter properties

	step 5.8 : create Servlet UI Copy from sir	
	




	
	



